Description:
    Generate a vuejs scope with webpacker convention.

    Including css, images, js folders in `src/[scope_name]`.
    - CSS will pre-config with **bulma CSS** framework
    - JS will including vue components folder, vuex setup, and initializers for rails side.

Example:
    rails generate espresso:vue:client

    This will create:
        app/javascripts/packs/client.js
        app/javascripts/src/client/
